title: [Fearling Pass, Rocky Trail]
description: The incline becomes a bit more challenging as the trail turns slightly and approaches the boundaries of the forest ahead.  A boulder or two provides the only respite from the sun and a place to rest or picnic.  Sloping downhill towards the north, the pass heads towards a glimmer of a lake in the distance.
